MESSAGE.value: Remove getLoader from column types.
Assign to category column the same type of the child enum.
Rebuild work again.
Close the reader after parsing the columns' names.
Framwork around ColumnTypeGuesser.
Refactor algorithm for ColumnTypeGuesser.
Remove unused helper classes for data series and loaders.
Change CategoryType to use a list of strings instead of an enumeration. Assign category values from the source file when a category is detected in the column.
Create a copy of the referenced category node when the reference is set from the inspector. Assign a name to each category node.
Show column type next to the colum in the editor. For categories, show the list of allowed values extracted from the data file.
Fix default type assigned to a column.
Restrict the selectable columns for charts to the ones with a numeric type.
Remove empty values from the column. Test and fix boolean column type.
Few tests after the merge.
Add migration script to assign a numeric type to untyped columns.
Apply migration script to existing delimited files.
Move root column types into an accessory model. Remove solution XChart/types.
Remove solution XChart/types from BaseLanguage solution.
Remove solution XChart/types from models inside BaseLanguage solution.
Fix NPE on DataFile's checking rule.

Add types language to avoid a bootstrap dependency within the XChart language. I'm temporary leaving the accessory model in the XChart language. It will be removed when all the tables in other projects will be migrated/relinked.
Remove types instances from the XChart language. Import the XChart/types as dependency.
Remove bootstrap dependency from XChart language.
Add XChart.types language to XChart plugin. Add mps settings aspect with bootstrap set to true.
Move types' concepts in the XChart.types language. Move the types' instances in the XChart language. Relink solutions.
